Company Overview
Newfound Research LLC, a financial technology and product innovation company, provides quantitative integrity solutions. It offers a disruptive approach to investment product design; private wealth management for high-net worth clients; and solutions for institutional investors. The company also works with portfolio managers of various types in co-developing investment strategies; and custom develops white-labeled model portfolios that align with financial advisory firms’ initiatives, outlooks, and clients’ needs. Newfound Research LLC has a strategic partnership with The NASDAQ OMX Group, Inc. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts.


